WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.633 --> 00:00:02.266
[music playing]

00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:08.600
WOMAN 1: For her time,
Dian was very exceptional.

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:11.233
Women wanted to get
married and have kids.

00:00:18.867 --> 00:00:23.900
Setting up Karisoke, and
studying the gorillas,

00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:26.500
and living that
whole kind of life

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:30.400
was completely not how
she was brought up.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:33.633
She was not raised in
an animal loving family.

00:00:33.633 --> 00:00:38.367
She followed her own
path very soon in life.

00:00:43.433 --> 00:00:46.533
MAN 1: She had aspirations to
work with animals as a vet,

00:00:46.533 --> 00:00:49.200
but she didn't get the grades.

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.767
So she ended up
working with children,

00:00:50.767 --> 00:00:54.800
as an occupational
therapist, which she did for,

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:56.700
must have been, 10 years.

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:59.033
So she'd already had
a successful career

00:00:59.033 --> 00:01:01.233
before this complete
change of direction.

00:01:04.967 --> 00:01:08.800
MAN 2: She wasn't doing it
to get academic credentials.

00:01:11.567 --> 00:01:13.200
WOMAN 1: The
paleoanthropologist,

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:16.900
Louis Leakey, was looking
for somebody to go start

00:01:16.900 --> 00:01:20.367
a long-term study of gorilla's.

00:01:20.367 --> 00:01:23.100
He had helped launch
Jane Goodall's career.

00:01:27.667 --> 00:01:29.333
WOMAN 2: I'd already
decided that I

00:01:29.333 --> 00:01:33.600
must study gorillas before
first meeting Dr. Leakey.

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.800
After a brief
interview, he suggested

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:39.133
that I become the gorilla
girl he had been seeking.

00:01:39.133 --> 00:01:41.567
And our conversation
ended with his assertion

00:01:41.567 --> 00:01:43.633
that I should have
my appendix removed

00:01:43.633 --> 00:01:49.400
before venturing into the remote
wilderness of Central Africa.

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.533
WOMAN 1: Leakey mentioned the
possibility of having to have

00:01:51.533 --> 00:01:54.867
her appendix out,
and she put herself

00:01:54.867 --> 00:01:57.533
right in for the operation.

00:01:57.533 --> 00:02:00.567
He was shocked, but,
clearly, it convinced

00:02:00.567 --> 00:02:03.066
him that this one might stick.

00:02:03.066 --> 00:02:05.800
She was very determined.

